data.description: Welcome to this stunning  5-bedroom, 2-bathroom farm ranch styled home! Boasting an array of features tailored for comfort and convenience, this residence offers a perfect blend of modern amenities and classic charm. Upon entry you'll be greeted by cathedral ceiling foyer that leads into your spacious living room. This beautiful home features a wood burning stove for those chilly days in addition to a fireplace in a separate room to enjoy. With generously sized bedrooms offering ample space on first and second floors, the possibilities are endless. The primary bedroom featuring a convenient walk-in closet for enhanced organization as well as possibility for an en-suite. Designed with modern living in mind, this home is equipped with custom large sliding doors that seamlessly blend indoor and outdoor spaces, creating an open and airy feel. In addition you will be able to entertain effortlessly with a fire pit nestled in the backyard, providing the ideal setting for gatherings with friends and family. The meticulously designed French drain in the yard ensures proper drainage, maintaining the pristine beauty of the outdoor space.  Additionally, enjoy the convenience of a generator hookup, ensuring peace of mind during power outages. Embrace the future with technology-enhanced living, featuring "Smart" locks and thermostats for added security and energy efficiency. Never worry about fumbling for keys again with a garage door opener simplifying your daily routines.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite residence your own! Huge Benefit, Sewers!
